  63:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_uart.c ****         the HAL_UART_Init() API.
  64:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_uart.c **** 
