  73:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_uart.c **** 
  74:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_uart.c ****     (#) For the UART RS485 Driver Enabled mode, initialize the UART registers
