 253:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_uart.c ****       (+) For the asynchronous mode the parameters below can be configured:
 254:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) Baud Rate
 255:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) Word Length
 256:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) Stop Bit
