ARM GAS  C:\Users\bku598\AppData\Local\Temp\ccXbpguR.s 			page 6


 258:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_uart.c ****              in the data register is transmitted but is changed by the parity bit.
 259:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) Hardware flow control
 260:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) Receiver/transmitter modes
 261:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) Over Sampling Method
 262:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) One-Bit Sampling Method
