 279:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_uart.c ****   Depending on the frame length defined by the M1 and M0 bits (7-bit,
 280:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_uart.c ****   8-bit or 9-bit), the possible UART formats are listed in the
 281:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_uart.c ****   following table.
 282:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_uart.c **** 
